00:25:17,851 --> 00:25:22,535
[SPEAKER_04]: And then there was a significant waiver section that was included.

177
00:25:22,555 --> 00:25:41,110
[SPEAKER_04]: I think we can discuss that in more detail in terms of the duties of a contracting department and the covered building service vendors that the contracts ensuring that it would include the anticipated number of hours of work for the employees.

