00:29:06,786 --> 00:29:09,288
[SPEAKER_04]: And then similarly around benefits,

196
00:29:13,069 --> 00:29:20,738
[SPEAKER_04]: It also ties it to the Department of Labor and the city of Boston employees who are doing similar work.

197
00:29:27,583 --> 00:29:29,665
[SPEAKER_04]: And I think that's pretty much everything.

198
00:29:30,165 --> 00:29:48,080
[SPEAKER_04]: In terms of complaints, there was just one change which is that a current or former employee could file a complaint and that the city would treat those complaints as confidential unless the employee consented to those complaints being shared with their employer.

