[SPEAKER_06]: But I don't think there's a dispute about that.

303
00:43:17,396 --> 00:43:19,917
[SPEAKER_06]: If there are questions about that, I'm happy to respond to them.

304
00:43:20,878 --> 00:43:21,879
[SPEAKER_06]: I hope that's of some help.

305
00:43:25,241 --> 00:43:25,761
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you, Peter.

