327
00:45:25,145 --> 00:45:28,786
[SPEAKER_06]: worker retention provisions and the labor peace protections.

328
00:45:29,586 --> 00:45:51,691
[SPEAKER_06]: It also, I was rather struck, and I think Councilor Bears was as well, by the rather wide waiver provisions that were proposed in the KP law draft that would have left the actual application of the ordinances protections very much up to case-by-case determinations.

329
00:45:51,771 --> 00:45:54,172
[SPEAKER_06]: Those are the primary things that I would note.

330
